OL,3,CEverything Starmer said in his latest
OL,4,Cupdate on Iran war
OL,6,FThe prime minister says he is
OL,7,F"standing firm" on the UK's military
OL,8,Fresponse to war in the Middle East,
OL,9,Fdespite "pressure to do otherwise."
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer gave an update on the
OL,12,FUK's response to the US-Israeli war on
OL,13,FIran at a press conference in Downing
OL,14,FStreet on Thursday afternoon.
OL,16,FHe announced he had chaired a Cobra
OL,17,Fmeeting on Thursday morning and said
OL,18,Fhe was focused on "providing calm,
OL,19,Flevel-headed leadership in the
OL,20,Fnational interest".
OL,26,@|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772745129
OL,3,CEverything Starmer said in his latest
OL,4,Cupdate on Iran war
OL,6,F"That means deploying our military and
OL,7,Fdiplomatic strength to protect our
OL,8,Fpeople, and it means having the
OL,9,Fstrength to stand firm by our values
OL,10,Fand our principles, no matter the
OL,11,Fpressure to do otherwise."
OL,13,FHe also insisted the UK had been
OL,14,Fpreparing for the possibility of
OL,15,Fconflict "long before" it began with
OL,16,FIsraeli and US strikes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@ZO]wD@JOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772745129
OL,3,CEverything Starmer said in his latest
OL,4,Cupdate on Iran war
OL,6,F"I know that people are worried sick
OL,7,Fabout their family and friends who are
OL,8,Fcaught up in this, about the impact on
OL,9,Four lives and our economy, and about
OL,10,Fthe potential for even greater
OL,11,Fescalation," he said.
OL,13,F"So, I want to reassure the British
OL,14,Fpublic about the action that we are
OL,15,Ftaking while the region has been
OL,16,Fplunged into chaos."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772745129
OL,3,CEverything Starmer said in his latest
OL,4,Cupdate on Iran war
OL,6,FThe PM also confirmed that the first
OL,7,Fgovernment charter flight from Oman
OL,8,Ftook off a few minutes before he began
OL,9,Fspeaking, after technical problems
OL,10,Fdelayed its departure last night.
OL,12,FHe announced the UK is sending four
OL,13,Fadditional Typhoon jets to join
OL,14,Foperations in Qatar.
OL,16,FThe PM also said he hasn't spoken to
OL,17,FTrump since the president's latest
OL,18,Fbroadside, where he said he was "not
OL,19,Fhappy" with Starmer over his decision
OL,20,Fnot to get involved in the initial
OL,21,Fstrikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
