CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772745129
OL,3,CEverything Starmer said in his latest
OL,4,Cupdate on Iran war
OL,6,FSpeaking in the Oval Office on Tuesday
OL,7,Fduring a visit from the German
OL,8,FChancellor, President Trump said:
OL,9,F"This is not Winston Churchill that
OL,10,Fwe're dealing with".
OL,12,FStarmer insisted the "special
OL,13,Frelationship is in operation right
OL,14,Fnow" after Trump's rebuke, adding that
OL,15,Fhe respected the US president taking
OL,16,Fdecisions which "he considers in the
OL,17,Fnational interest" of America.
OL,26,@tD@VOUvD@DO]xD@QOUyD@RO]
