OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe PM said he was "satisfied that we
OL,12,Fcan keep our people safe" as he faced
OL,13,Fquestions about the UK's preparedness
OL,14,Fover the Middle East conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
