OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772745129
OL,3,CEverything Starmer said in his latest
OL,4,Cupdate on Iran war
OL,6,FAsked about criticism that the
OL,7,Fgovernment's approach had been marked
OL,8,Fby indecision and a lack of
OL,9,Fpreparedness, the PM said Britain
OL,10,F"started pre-deploying to the region
OL,11,Fin January and February, particularly
OL,12,Fto Cyprus and Qatar".
OL,14,F"There's been a lot of pre-planning
OL,15,Fgone into this, a lot of pre-
OL,16,Fdeployment that's gone into this," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
