PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772745129
OL,3,CEverything Starmer said in his latest
OL,4,Cupdate on Iran war
OL,6,FThe PM was also pressed on reports
OL,7,Fthat Ed Miliband and other members of
OL,8,Fthe Cabinet opposed British support
OL,9,Ffor pre-emptive military action during
OL,10,Fa meeting on Friday.
OL,12,FStarmer insisted the US didn't request
OL,13,Fthe use of UK military bases until
OL,14,FSaturday afternoon, "therefore, on
OL,15,FFriday, there was no concrete decision
OL,16,Fto be made."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772745129
OL,3,CEverything Starmer said in his latest
OL,4,Cupdate on Iran war
OL,6,F"A decision had to be made when we had
OL,7,Fthe request, that came in on Saturday
OL,8,Fduring the course of the afternoon `
OL,9,Fwe were already taking measures in
OL,10,Frelation to our own capability ` that
OL,11,Fcame in on Saturday afternoon, late in
OL,12,Fthe afternoon.
OL,14,F"We then, as you would have expected,
OL,15,Fwent through the details with the US
OL,16,Fover the next day, and ultimately
OL,17,Freached a decision on Sunday, which I
OL,18,Fannounced then on Sunday evening,
OL,19,Fabout eight or nine o'clock.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
