OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772745129
OL,3,CEverything Starmer said in his latest
OL,4,Cupdate on Iran war
OL,6,F"But actually, on Friday, we didn't
OL,7,Fhave a request from the United States,
OL,8,Fand therefore no decision fell to be
OL,9,Fmade."
